    "description": "An FEA model is used to predict peak von Mises stress and stress distribution in the tibial tray of a total knee replacement under physiological gait loading. Model influence is MODERATE (model supplements bench testing); decision consequence is MODERATE (incorrect prediction could contribute to premature fatigue failure but is mitigated by physical testing requirements). Model Risk Level 3 per the Nagaraja assessment framework.",
