      "rationale": "The FEA solver (Abaqus 2022) is a commercially validated code with documented V&V reports. Internal SQA procedures include version-controlled input decks, automated regression test suite (47 benchmark cases), and documented change control. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for MRL 3 Class II applications."
