      "rationale": "Code verification performed against NAFEMS benchmark problems LE1 (plane stress) and LE10 (3D solid stress). Abaqus C3D10 element formulation verified against analytical Lamé solutions for thick-walled cylinder under internal pressure. All benchmark errors < 1.5%. Achieved level 2 meets the required level 2 for MRL 3."
