      "rationale": "Systematic mesh refinement study (ValidationResult vr003) demonstrates GCI < 2.1% for peak von Mises stress on the production mesh. Richardson extrapolation applied following Roache (1998) methodology. Contact zone mesh sensitivity separately verified. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
