      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-test-samples-criteria",
      "rationale": "Validation dataset includes five tibial tray specimens from the same production lot as the COU device, plus five synthetic bone composite specimens per ASTM F1839. Sample size justification documented based on expected coefficient of variation from historical data. Specimen dimensional inspection records confirm conformance to design drawings. Inter-specimen variability quantified and incorporated in validation uncertainty budget. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
