      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-equivalency-criteria",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment performed comparing validation model inputs to COU model inputs across all material, geometric, and loading parameters. Equivalency matrix documented with quantitative similarity scores. Key differences identified (cadaveric vs. synthetic bone substrate in subset of tests) and their effect on QOI quantified via matched-pair analysis showing < 7% systematic offset, within accepted uncertainty budget. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
